PyBZEngine is a simple 3D engine library, most of which
was originally developed for the PyBZFlag project. It
makes heavy use of PyOpenGL and Numeric.

Key features:
  - Simple but effective Drawable model
  - Easily extensible particle systems
  - Cloth simulation
  - High quality scalable and hinted text rendering
  - Perlin noise
  - Easy sequencing of multiple scenes, with transitions
  - Spiffy sky
  - In-game movie recorder

--Micah Dowty <micah@picogui.org>
